data.description: One Owner in this 55+ Community. Fabulous upgrades in this home make it a MUST see.  350k FHA 3% assumable note for qualified buyers!! Two outdoor living spaces one in the front patio area AND a pavestone patio in the back.  Still allowing green space for fur babies and grandchildren to roam. You will see storage everywhere, open concept kitchen with stainless & granite, wood floors and tile throughout, a wonderful master suite and gorgeous brick and stone exteriors. Not often do homes in this niche community become available.  Did we mention the magnolia trees lining the streets and the security gate which keeps watch on these homes! Affordable HOA maintains grounds including backyard area and creates a - secure lock and leave - environment. They will even plant for you if you provide plants! Don't miss the swimming pool! Minutes from downtown Fort Worth and Hulen area, Clearfork shopping and state of the art medical facilities. You are guaranteed to LOVE the outdoor patios! Come see!
